headline: Fastenal and the Belfast Giants Enter Sponsorship Agreement
summary: WINONA, Minn. & BELFAST, Northern Ireland, December 18, 2025--Fastenal Company (Nasdaq: FAST), a global leader in industrial distribution and supply chain solutions, and the Belfast Giants, the only professional ice hockey team on the island of Ireland, have entered into a sponsorship agreement to enhance Fastenal's brand exposure in Northern Ireland.
